{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"151fafeb4e","title":"给文南松的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d374d9361","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"151fafeb4e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"6b6e318952","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文南松，毛泽东的表兄。2]运昌，即文运昌，毛泽东的表兄。"},{"id":"5880c507cf","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"十哥，即文洋香，毛泽东的表兄。十七哥，即文枚清，毛泽东的表兄。"},{"id":"ffcc41f8a5","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"十一哥，即文润泉，毛泽东的表兄。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a2a5c7edc0","type":"title","text":"给文南松\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"},{"id":"6b6e318952","type":"paragraph","text":"南松表兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"},{"id":"5880c507cf","type":"paragraph","text":"正月来信收到了，感谢你的好意。运昌以兑给我多次信，我回了一信，寄南县白蚌口，不知他收到没有？运昌兄的工作，不宜由我推荐，宜由他自己在人民中有所表现，取得信任，便有机会参加工作。十哥、十七哥还在否？十一哥健在甚感，他有信来，我已回了一信，不知他收到否？你说乡里缺粮，政府不发，不知现在怎么样，还是缺粮吗？政府一点办法也没想吗？来信时请详为告我","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"},{"id":"ffcc41f8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"此复，即间近安！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"},{"id":"e7e4b50336","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"},{"id":"b27c3dbdf5","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年五月十二日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e"}],"page":{"id":"4a4253e885","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"151fafeb4e","start":373,"end":373}}}},"__N_SSG":true}